{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 I am {\b Junki Kim}, a game sound designer. This script is a dedicated audio visualization tool for REAPER. As I am not a professional programmer, I may not be perfect at fixing every error or bug, but I am always open to feedback! If you have any suggestions or improvements, please feel free to email me.\par}
